  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 180°C (350°F).",
    "Place bread slices on a baking sheet and bake for about 2 minutes or until lightly toasted.",
    "In a mixing bowl, combine toasted bread crumbs with chopped nuts, spices, coconut flour, milk chocolate chips, eggs, and yogurt. Mix well to form a crumble mixture.",
    "Press the crumble mixture onto each slice of toast and bake in oven for an additional 5-7 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "Serve hot as a breakfast dish."
